{"tid":2371023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自製天然酵母，用生果做種","createTime":"2021-01-18T12:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T10:12:31.000Z","uid":132749,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4423ff09c875f841a917950ea5c1e42a5047ddf2","tid":2371023,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"之前試話用麵粉整天然酵母，整完之後上網睇到好多人用生果去做種， 所以都試下整<br />\n<br />\n一開始用提子乾整過，但唔成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要整左兩次都無泡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGSV53T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGSV53T.jpg&h=d96d74cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後用新鮮生果整，咁岩屋企買左好多apricot, 就事但拎左幾粒黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8nKZp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8nKZp1.jpg&h=dd7faa3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EicSoRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEicSoRH.jpg&h=2162177a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENppZp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENppZp3.jpg&h=5870e292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整完放左幾日，開始愈黎愈多泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2w7XbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2w7XbY.jpg&h=9a6b3bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsbscLj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsbscLj.jpg&h=8a2cf83a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xM0D3R0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxM0D3R0.jpg&h=5e3cb7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後用酵母液去整麵種發得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBDKeY6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBDKeY6.jpg&h=961e0938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q9LZ3VD8liE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq9LZ3VD8liE&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=0b4c6a7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q9LZ3VD8liE</a><br />\n<br />\n今次宜個酵母比就咁用麵粉養易好多，仲有出黎有好香既果香， 唔一定用apricot, 用其他生果都得。 試過用黎整包，效果都好好，當然愈耐個種發酵得愈好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既記得subscribe, like 同share 我YouTube Channel,仲有follow 我ig <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=5d0e16f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fopenfridge_kitchendiary%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c651265c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/</a><br />\n<br />\nMEWE:<a href=\"https://mewe.com/i/openfridgekitchendiary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fi%2Fopenfridgekitchendiary&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=1964bce0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/i/openfridgekitchendiary</a>"},{"pid":"385f24ddc7ccf4b874f0ae54cfd58678c9144cce","tid":2